His slim, black pants tucked into his boots give the outfit a sleek, modern feel, while his long, brown scarf adds a touch of classic elegance to the look. On his head sits a wide-brimmed, brown leather hat with copper accents, and around his neck, he wears a glowing amulet that seems to pulse with magical energy.
